  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK343">
<l>aṭalvēṇṭu maintaṉ pulattai viṭalvēṇṭum</l>
<l>vēṇṭiya vellā moruṅku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the five senses be destroyed; and at the same time, let everything be abandoned that (the ascetic) has (formerly) desired.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
